                                                 [sudoers-user creation]
1. useradd masthan    [whenever we create user "group & folder" automatically created]
2. passwd masthan
   ** ** ** [give password]
3. visudo (or) vim /etc/sudoers (line-100)
   masthan    ALL=(ALL)       ALL
4. su - masthan 

5. sudo useradd baji (if we can create user it's working)

commands:
cat /etc/passwd  : to show list of users
cat /etc/group	 : to show list of groups
userdel masthan  : to delete Vijay user
groupdel masthan : to delete Vijay group
   


